# ============================================================================
# bleu.live — .gitignore
# Comprehensive Node + Python coverage. Closes TD-006 / FU-005 / Week 1 W1.4.
# Audit ref: _meta/audit/2026-05-21/09_SECURITY_AND_PRIVACY_AUDIT.md
# ============================================================================

# ---- preserved from prior .gitignore -----------------------------------------
.github/workflows/deploy-alvai.yml
docs/cleanup-may-2026/

# Supabase CLI local state — created by `supabase link`. Contains
# project-ref metadata and may contain access tokens / cache. Must not
# be committed.
.supabase/
supabase/.temp/
# Note: a handful of files inside supabase/.temp/ are already tracked
# from before this rule was added (cli-latest, gotrue-version, etc.).
# They will continue to show as modified after every supabase CLI
# invocation. Untracking is a separate cleanup (`git rm --cached`).

# ---- environment / secrets ---------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
secrets/
credentials.json
service-account*.json

